websockets are a communication protocol that enables two way(bi-directional) communication between applications.
websockets are great choice when we want two way communication.
websockets are well suited when you need to puch freash data as soon as it is available on the server.
unlike HTTP that are short lived , websockets enables the connection in realtime as long-lived for real time communication.
it maintains the connection ,, until it closed from the either side.as they maintains long-lived connections as not causes any memory problem. 